snippet.textDisplay: So the red scarf represents memories of the time spent together, care and belongingness. Train represents life which moves on as the person who fell in love in the beginning without being able to express, moved on after leaving the memories of unspoken love and feelings behind. While the girl gathered those memories in the end when she picked up the red scarf it was too late by that time as she couldn't express her feelings. The other characters represent envy, misunderstandings and jealousy.
